  "title": "Transitions to adulthood in urban Kenya",
  "abstract": "Migration is often intrinsically tied to key adolescent transitions in sub-Saharan Africa. However, while many adolescents move in order to improve their life trajectories, migration may also coincide with new challenges and considerable disruption of family support.",
